        <!-- ===== walkthrough legend ===== -->
        <mxCell id="legend" value="Demo walkthrough — ./demo/README.md&#10;&#10;①  ./scripts/prepare.sh  → keystores + service jars + Keycloak realm&#10;②  ./demo/up.sh  — boots the 13-container stack (12-service base + demo-seed),&#10;      blocks until one batch sits at PENDING_REGISTRAR&#10;③  http://localhost:8081  — log in as registrar1, open the batch, click &quot;Approve or reject&quot;&#10;      → the UI POSTs {&quot;decision&quot;:&quot;APPROVE&quot;,&quot;rejectedDocumentIds&quot;:[]}&#10;④  log out, log in as dean1, Approve the same batch (a premature dean click → 409)&#10;⑤  wait ~2 min — cumulative saga cost: 3 CSC round-trips, Kafka hops + outbox&#10;      relay poll, FOP render + veraPDF gate.  Not a TSA.  Reload /monitor to see COMPLETED.&#10;⑥  MinIO console :9001  — transcript-pdfs/ + signed-transcripts/&#10;&#10;./demo/smoke.sh  asserts ≥1 PENDING_REGISTRAR   ·   ./demo/down.sh  stops + wipes volumes" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontFamily=Noto Sans JP;fontSize=12;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=10;fillColor=#f5f5f5;strokeColor=#b0b0b0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
